  m_Name: QuestionChoice6
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: The Wolf points toward a dark, unpainted corner of the canvas. "I found
    a patch of Stardust Flowers that the Merchant doesn't know about. It's far away
    and very dark, but follow me alone and I'll show you."
  option1: I never go to dark, unknown places without my guardian or a trusted adult
    knowing where I am.
  option2: "More flowers would help the Eternal Garden grow! Lead the way, I\u2019ll
    follow you."
  option3: "I'll go with you, but I\u2019ll leave a trail of wheat so I can find
    my way back later."
